data.description: This beautiful 1 Story, 4 Bed/2 Bath, has a freshly painted interior with a formal dining, study, open floor plan with a fireplace and high ceilings offering plenty of natural light throughout the home. The kitchen features a stainless-steel dishwasher, gas cooktop, built in oven, granite countertops with tile backsplash, 42-inch mocha cabinets with plenty of counter space and has a large granite island. It opens up to the living room and dinning area with a beautiful accent wall. The Primary suite has a large bathroom with a garden tub and separate shower with a huge walk-in closet. The entire house has pristine upgraded hardwood flooring and tile throughout with absolutely NO CARPET! The laundry room has a new laundry table that's great for folding clothes and provides a convenient work surface. Fresh landscaping and expanded covered patio that is great for having family or entertainment. Just minutes from downtown Boerne, gyms, restaurants, parks, schools and 20 minutes from San Antonio. This home is move in ready and waiting for you to call it HOME!
